  class="mainContainer grid justify-center gap-12 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3"
>
  <div>
    <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg">Expertise</h2>
    <p>
      Our team of highly skilled and experienced structural engineers possesses
      a deep understanding of the complexities of structural design. We bring a
      wealth of knowledge to every project, ensuring that our solutions are
      reliable, efficient, and tailored to meet your specific needs.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg">Innovative Solutions</h2>
    <p>
      We thrive on pushing the boundaries of what's possible in structural
      engineering. Our consultants utilize cutting-edge technologies and
      industry-leading practices to deliver innovative solutions that optimize
      performance, minimize costs, and exceed your expectations.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg">Commitment to Quality</h2>
    <p>
      Quality is at the heart of everything we do. We adhere to stringent
